Package com.salesforce.multicloudj.sts.driver

Class AbstractSts<T extends AbstractSts<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.salesforce.multicloudj.sts.driver.AbstractSts<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Provider
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AliSts, AwsSts, GcpSts
    public abstract class AbstractSts<T extends AbstractSts<T>>
extends Object
implements Provider
    Abstract base class for Security Token Service (STS) implementations. This class is internal for SDK and all the providers for STS implementations are supposed to implement it.
